#### SECTION 2 — What It Means to Be [Stage]

**Purpose:** Explain what this frontend stage represents as a whole — the posture, the challenges, the opportunity. This is stage-level context, not sub-stage specific.

| UI Element | View Field | Notes |
|---|---|---|
