## Part 4 — Relationship to Results Overview Tab

The Stage Context tab is the second of two pill toggle views on the Results Dashboard. It is intentionally separate from the Results Overview tab and shares no components with it. The two tabs:

- Use different data sources: Results Overview queries `vw_ae_dashboard_results`, Stage Context queries `vw_ae_stage_context`
- Serve different purposes: Results Overview is personalized diagnostic output, Stage Context is orientation and framework context
- Share the same assessment ID as their query key

The CTA block in Stage Context (directing to the M&R Audit) is the primary conversion bridge between the AE Ladder assessment layer and the next tier of the platform.